                        <li>Unable to provide history (dementia)</li>
                        <li>CXR: Bibasilar opacities</li>
                        <li>Started IV antibiotics, improved</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">Day 5 - Left AMA</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Alert & oriented × 3, had capacity</li>
                        <li>Family wanted placement</li>
                        <li>Patient refused: "Tired of hospital"</li>
                        <li>Discharged on oral antibiotics</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">48 Hours Later - Re-presentation</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Found somnolent by neighbors</li>
                        <li>SpO2 84% on room air</li>
                        <li>Initially hypotensive (BP 65/45)</li>
                        <li>Transferred to our facility</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="critical-box">
                <p><strong>Context:</strong> Lives alone, progressive dementia, medication non-compliance, still driving</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SLIDE 3 -->
        <div class="slide">
            <h1>Laboratory Data (Day 1)</h1>
            <div class="two-column">
                <div class="content-section">
                    <h3>Complete Blood Count</h3>
